      <title>印尼新总统面临 1860 亿美元债务困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/indonesia-s-new-president-faces-186-billion-debt-dilemma</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执掌东南亚最大经济体几天后，印尼总统需要制定计划来应对背负 1,860 亿美元债务的重点国有企业不断上升的借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/indonesia-s-new-president-faces-186-billion-debt-dilemma</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宏利财富和资产管理部门裁员 2.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/manulife-cuts-2-5-of-staff-in-wealth-and-asset-management-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宏利金融公司 (Manulife Financial Corp.) 已在其全球财富和资产管理业务中裁减了数百个工作岗位，约占该部门员工总数的 2.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/manulife-cuts-2-5-of-staff-in-wealth-and-asset-management-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 21:46:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超微审计师安永在审查期间辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/super-micro-auditor-e-y-resigned-amid-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为 Super Micro Computers 提供审计服务的安永会计师事务所因对 Super Micro 管理团队的道德问题表示担忧而辞职，导致这家服务器公司的股价大幅下跌。Super Micro 以与戴尔和惠普一起组装服务器而闻名，在这些问题出现之前，其股价大幅上涨。彭博科技的 Edward Ludlow 与 Sonali Basak 在“彭博市场”节目中讨论了该公司不确定的未来。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/super-micro-auditor-e-y-resigned-amid-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 21:09:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师 Thill 称 Meta 的支出将获得回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/meta-s-spending-will-pay-off-analyst-thill-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Jefferies 分析师 Brent Thill 表示，Meta Platforms Inc. 的资本支出将在“彭博收盘”中得到回报。Meta 预计假日季度销售额将强于预期，并大力宣传其核心广告业务的人工智能改进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/meta-s-spending-will-pay-off-analyst-thill-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 21:03:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Roku 将停止报告季度用户数量；股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/roku-to-stop-reporting-user-numbers-shares-tumble</link>
      <description><![CDATA[流媒体电视机顶盒制造商 Roku Inc. 表示，从明年开始，它将不再报告每季度使用其产品的家庭数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/roku-to-stop-reporting-user-numbers-shares-tumble</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 20:52:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西门子同意以 100 亿美元收购软件集团 Altair</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/siemens-agrees-to-buy-software-group-altair-in-10-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西门子股份公司已同意以 100 亿美元（包括债务）收购软件制造商 Altair Engineering Inc.，这笔交易将进一步推动这家德国工程巨头向利润率更高的软件驱动产品线转型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/siemens-agrees-to-buy-software-group-altair-in-10-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 20:51:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 季度业绩低于预期，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/coinbase-turns-profitable-as-revenue-doubles-during-crypto-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的加密货币交易所 Coinbase Global Inc. 公布的业绩低于华尔街预期，尽管收入几乎翻了一番，但其股价在尾盘交易中下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/coinbase-turns-profitable-as-revenue-doubles-during-crypto-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 20:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 因比特币减值费用连续第三次亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/microstrategy-posts-third-straight-loss-on-bitcoin-impairment-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币对冲基金代理公司 MicroStrategy Inc. 在对其约 180 亿美元的加密货币储备计提减值准备后，连续第三个季度出现亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/microstrategy-posts-third-straight-loss-on-bitcoin-impairment-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 20:14:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马拉松石油公司在康菲石油公司收购前裁减休斯顿 500 个工作岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/marathon-oil-cuts-500-houston-jobs-amid-conocophillips-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据州政府文件显示，马拉松石油公司警告称，作为康菲石油公司 170 亿美元收购计划的一部分，其休斯顿总部将进行“大规模裁员”，涉及 500 多名员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/marathon-oil-cuts-500-houston-jobs-amid-conocophillips-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 19:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
